## Limitations
The findings are based on available data and literature, which may not cover all aspects of the debate. The search was limited to English-language sources and may not reflect global perspectives comprehensively. Additionally, the dynamic nature of public health policies means that recommendations and mandates can change, potentially affecting the relevance of the findings over time.